para_trans: Provisional promotion and posting of Assistant Engineer, Grade and Branch Engineer (Architecture) in Zilla Parishad to the post of Deputy Assistant Engineer (Architecture) at the establishment of Maharashtra Life Authority. - A clean sheet.
Government Corrigendum No: ZIPGRA-1224 / P.No.152 / PAPU-23
7th Floor, Gokuldas Tejpal Hospital Building Complex
Near Crawford Maket, Lokmanya Tilak Marg, Mumbai-400001
1) GOVERNMENT ORDER No. ZIPGRA-1224 / P.No.152 / PAPU-23, dated 15.10.2024.
Branch Engineer (Architecture) in Zilla Parishad to be appointed by Maharashtra Life Authority.
Subject to the order in respect of the post of Deputy Assistant (Construction) from the Zilla Parishad quota at the establishment.
A temporary promotion has been made. Promoted from the Branch Engineer cadre in the said order.
The name of the officer at A.No. (4) is "Mr. B.K. Balkhande "instead of" Mr. D.K. Balkhande. "
This Government Corrigendum is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
